'''Apple S1'''是第一代[[蘋果手錶|蘋果手錶]]（Apple Watch）中的整合式電腦晶片，蘋果公司形容其為「[[SiP|系統型封裝]]」（SiP）<ref name="ApplePR">{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2014/09/09Apple-Unveils-Apple-Watch-Apples-Most-Personal-Device-Ever.html|title=Apple Unveils Apple Watch|publisher=Apple Inc.|accessdate=2014-10-08|archive-date=2014-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008211005/https://www.apple.com/pr/library/2014/09/09Apple-Unveils-Apple-Watch-Apples-Most-Personal-Device-Ever.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

據報導[[三星電子|三星]]是S1核心組件的供應商，提供包括[[隨機存取記憶體|隨機存取記憶體]]（RAM）、[[闪存#NAND_Flash|NAND Flash]]儲存裝置，以及組裝零件<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.macrumors.com/2015/01/09/samsung-produce-apple-watch-components/ |title=Samsung Supposedly Wins Orders to Produce Apple Watch Components |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2015-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150430080206/http://www.macrumors.com/2015/01/09/samsung-produce-apple-watch-components/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 系統型封裝設計 ==
S1使用整合了[[隨機存取記憶體|隨機存取記憶體]]、[[快閃記憶體|儲存裝置]]和無線連結處理器的客製[[系統單晶片|系統單晶片]]，此外感應器和[[I/O|I/O]]裝置也整合其中。單晶片據傳加入了[[樹脂|樹脂]]填充以增加其耐用度<ref name="AppleTech">{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/watch/technology/|title=Apple.com - Apple Watch - Technology|work=Apple|accessdate=2014-10-08|archive-date=2014-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008025315/http://www.apple.com/watch/technology/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然關於此晶片的詳細資訊十分有限，但Chipwork網站指出其負責Wi-Fi和藍芽的處理器是[[Broadcom|Broadcom]]的BCM4334晶片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chipworks.com/en/technical-competitive-analysis/resources/blog/broadcom-wins-wifi-in-apple-watch/|title=Broadcom Wins WiFi in Apple Watch?|publisher=Chipworks|accessdate=2014-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006085240/http://www.chipworks.com/en/technical-competitive-analysis/resources/blog/broadcom-wins-wifi-in-apple-watch/|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。該處理器位於整塊系統單晶片的上方中央位置。

== 發表 ==
Apple S1是在2014年9月9日的「Wish we could say more.」發表會上與蘋果手錶共同公開。

== 推出日期 ==
Apple S1將隨著蘋果手錶在2015年4月正式上市<ref name="ApplePR"/><ref name="15Q1Earnings">{{Cite web |url=http://www.macrumors.com/2015/01/27/tim-cook-apple-watch-on-schedule-to-ship-in-april/ |title=Tim Cook: Apple Watch on Schedule to Ship in April |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2015-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404001009/http://www.macrumors.com/2015/01/27/tim-cook-apple-watch-on-schedule-to-ship-in-april/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

